thread.title: Richard

author: Richard
title: Richard
text:
I walked in with my papers, was met at the front desk immediately, had my mistakes corrected, immediately met with a clerk who verified my information, took photos, finished the application, and I was out in about 15 minutes.
The passport arrived on the date promised. I called a courier service and had the passport delivered to my office.
No fuss, no hassle. Very professional.
